{"tid":2044928,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[文化歷史台]第四講：近代喪屍電影起源與轉變","createTime":"2020-05-31T12:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T16:48:50.000Z","uid":74954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb8c646df72d64eb76d7c71eddbff6c363ae4eb","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"前言：喪屍電影年年出，而家大家見到以獵食為主既喪屍概念其實係近代先出現，以前既年代喪屍形態大家又知唔知呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG2hLmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG2hLmb.jpg&h=4ec13311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n課程連結<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eHEpTaKPJao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeHEpTaKPJao&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdNArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=873b72d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eHEpTaKPJao</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n本課重點：<br />\n1.喪屍概念既發源地-原來同黑人牙膏抬棺舞既起源係同一發源地<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGqfw2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGqfw2f.jpg&h=1a3acf33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh66DHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh66DHi.jpg&h=b8be831a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.felicia felix mentor喪屍真實案件 <br />\n海地傳說案故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTxJFYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTxJFYD.jpg&h=52f67a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漸漸呢d既神話 傳統同故事之後傳到去西方<br />\n帶入左西方既影視文化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.喪屍電影初期既形態-速度慢 樣貌呆滯 唔食肉 低侵略性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUjW0WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUjW0WU.jpg&h=a5affafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.近代喪屍電影之轉變原因 - 因為受一套the night of walking dead大賣而影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yie77B8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyie77B8.jpg&h=052297e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.對近幾年喪屍文化影視之反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwTEejn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwTEejn.jpg&h=45a6a8c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50ab19c7695f00a29ca0f0de212870804a081e5d","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"自推一下先"},{"pid":"1b3936e7566a2882503b7c01889816aa6c77f56f","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe089ad506fc12d5b4bba1f2cc3e5f6b3b0a5cbd","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3092b159da6854cb25001acf86a341e515ead13b","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263cfa69354a643b4c364872f5fb2701bf262d49","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b3a3e3203d86dc233db2c66789150ea72b030aa","tid":2044928,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl